getBlobStreamHandler

public static org.apache.commons.dbutils.ResultSetHandler getBlobStreamHandler()
Returns aResultSetHandler that returns the first column of the first row of a ResultSet as a BLOB. The contents of the BLOB will be returned as an InputStream.
